Be a US Citizen. NO non-citizens will be considered. 
Be capable of obtaining a DOD Secret Security Clearance, at a minimum. 
Preferred Qualifications 
Experience with Adversarial Machine Learning. 
Experience with Active or Interactive Machine Learning. 
Experience with human subjects research, user studies, or UX design and testing. 
Experience in a research environment. 
Cognitive modeling/ intelligent agent experience. 
Experience using High Performance Computing or Cloud Computing. 
Active and current DOD Secret Security Clearance 
